1992
02:18:23.070 --> 02:18:25.200
Do any thing but this thou doest.

1993
02:18:25.200 --> 02:18:27.700
Empty old receptacles, or common shores, of filth;

1994
02:18:27.700 --> 02:18:29.800
Serve by indenture to the common hangman:

1995
02:18:29.800 --> 02:18:32.900
Any of these ways are yet better than this;

1996
02:18:32.900 --> 02:18:39.970
For what thou professest, a baboon, could he speak,

1997
02:18:39.970 --> 02:18:46.300
Would own a name too dear. O, that the gods

1998
02:18:46.300 --> 02:18:49.500
Would safely deliver me from this place!

1999
02:18:55.800 --> 02:18:58.870
Here, here's gold for thee.

2000
02:18:58.870 --> 02:19:01.030
