2003
02:19:07.330 --> 02:19:10.730
And I will undertake all these to teach.

2004
02:19:16.900 --> 02:19:18.700
I doubt not but this populous city will

2005
02:19:18.700 --> 02:19:21.570
Yield many scholars.

2006
02:19:29.500 --> 02:19:34.230
