2007
02:19:34.230 --> 02:19:37.670
Prove that I cannot, take me home again,

2008
02:19:37.670 --> 02:19:39.930
And prostitute me to the basest groom

2009
02:19:39.930 --> 02:19:44.200
That doth frequent your house.

2010
02:19:51.700 --> 02:19:56.830
Well, I will see what I can do for thee:

2011
02:19:56.830 --> 02:19:58.470
if I can place thee, I will.

2012
02:19:58.470 --> 02:20:02.170
But amongst honest women.

2013
02:20:02.170 --> 02:20:07.430
'Faith, my acquaintance lies little amongst them.

2014
02:20:07.430 --> 02:20:10.570
But since my master and mistress have bought you,

2015
02:20:10.570 --> 02:20:14.170
there's no going but by their consent:

2016
02:20:14.170 --> 02:20:18.900
therefore I will make them acquainted with your purpose,

2017
02:20:18.900 --> 02:20:23.530
and I doubt not but I shall find them tractable enough.

2018
02:20:28.570 --> 02:20:36.170
Come, I'll do for thee what I can; come your ways.

2019
02:20:48.730 --> 02:20:52.470


2020
02:21:16.570 --> 02:21:20.770
Marina thus the brothel 'scapes, and enters

2021
02:21:20.770 --> 02:21:24.670
Into an honest house, our story says.

2022
02:21:24.670 --> 02:21:28.470
She sings like one immortal, and she dances

2023
02:21:28.470 --> 02:21:31.800
As goddess-like to her admired lays;

2024
02:21:31.800 --> 02:21:37.170
Deep clerks she dumbs; and with her needle composes

2025
02:21:37.170 --> 02:21:41.970
Nature's own shape, of bud, bird, branch, and berry,

2026
02:21:41.970 --> 02:21:46.230
That even her art sisters the natural roses;

2027
02:21:46.230 --> 02:21:49.430
Her inkle, silk, twin with the rubied cherry:

2028
02:21:49.430 --> 02:21:52.200
That pupils lacks she none of noble race,

2029
02:21:52.200 --> 02:21:55.700
Who pour their bounty on her; and her gain

2030
02:21:55.700 --> 02:22:02.030
She gives the cursed bawd. Here we her place;

2031
02:22:02.570 --> 02:22:04.870
And to her father turn our minds again,

2032
02:22:04.870 --> 02:22:08.200
Where we left him, on the sea. We there him lost;

2033
02:22:08.200 --> 02:22:11.730
Whence, driven before the winds, he is arrived

2034
02:22:11.730 --> 02:22:16.230
Here where his daughter dwells; and on this coast

2035
02:22:16.230 --> 02:22:20.430
Suppose him now at anchor. The city strived

2036
02:22:20.430 --> 02:22:23.630
God Neptune's annual feast to keep: from whence

2037
02:22:23.630 --> 02:22:28.400
Lysimachus our Tyrian ship espies,

2038
02:22:28.400 --> 02:22:32.830
His banners sable, trimm'd with rich expense;

2039
02:22:32.830 --> 02:22:37.330
And to him in his barge with fervor hies.

2040
02:22:37.630 --> 02:22:39.500
Where is lord Helicanus?

2041
02:22:39.500 --> 02:22:40.730
he can resolve you.

2042
02:22:40.730 --> 02:22:41.730
O, here he is.

2043
02:22:41.730 --> 02:22:44.270
Sir, there's a barge put off from Mytilene,

2044
02:22:44.270 --> 02:22:46.170
And in it is Lysimachus the governor,

2045
02:22:46.170 --> 02:22:47.970
Who craves to come aboard. What is your will?

2046
02:22:47.970 --> 02:22:50.370
That he have his. Call up some gentlemen.

2047
02:22:50.370 --> 02:22:53.170
Ho, gentlemen! my lord calls.

2048
02:22:56.730 --> 02:22:59.900
Gentlemen, there's some of worth would come aboard;

2049
02:22:59.900 --> 02:23:02.370
I pray ye, greet them fairly.

2050
02:23:03.600 --> 02:23:04.800
Sir,

2051
02:23:04.800 --> 02:23:08.130
This is the man that can, in aught you would, resolve you.

2052
02:23:08.130 --> 02:23:11.970
Hail, reverend sir! the gods preserve you!

2053
02:23:11.970 --> 02:23:14.300
And you, sir, to outlive the age I am,

2054
02:23:14.300 --> 02:23:16.100
And die as I would do.

2055
02:23:16.100 --> 02:23:18.570
You wish me well.

2056
02:23:18.570 --> 02:23:22.070
Being on shore, honouring of Neptune's triumphs,

2057
02:23:22.070 --> 02:23:24.700
Seeing this goodly vessel ride before us,

2058
02:23:24.700 --> 02:23:27.030
I made to it, to know of whence you are.

2059
02:23:27.030 --> 02:23:29.300
First, what is your place?

2060
02:23:29.300 --> 02:23:32.330
I am the governor of this place you lie before.

2061
02:23:32.330 --> 02:23:34.200
Sir,

2062
02:23:34.200 --> 02:23:39.700
Our vessel is of Tyre, in it the king;

2063
02:23:39.700 --> 02:23:42.030
A man who for this three months hath not spoken

2064
02:23:42.030 --> 02:23:45.000
To any one, nor taken sustenance

2065
02:23:45.000 --> 02:23:47.230
But to prorogue his grief.

2066
02:23:47.230 --> 02:23:49.730
Upon what ground is his distemperature?

2067
02:23:49.730 --> 02:23:51.100
'Twould be too tedious to repeat;

2068
02:23:51.100 --> 02:23:52.270
But the main grief springs from the loss

2069
02:23:52.270 --> 02:23:55.200
Of a beloved daughter and a wife.

2070
02:23:55.200 --> 02:23:57.030
May we not see him?

2071
02:23:57.030 --> 02:23:58.200
You may;

2072
02:23:58.200 --> 02:24:01.230
But bootless is your sight: he will not speak to any.

2073
02:24:01.230 --> 02:24:04.230
Yet let me obtain my wish.

2074
02:24:14.400 --> 02:24:16.900
Behold him.

2075
02:24:16.900 --> 02:24:18.730
This was a goodly person,

2076
02:24:18.730 --> 02:24:21.030
Till the disaster that, one mortal night,

2077
02:24:21.030 --> 02:24:24.100
Drove him to this.

2078
02:24:27.230 --> 02:24:32.300
Sir king, all hail!

2079
02:24:32.300 --> 02:24:36.570
Hail, royal sir!

2080
02:24:45.200 --> 02:24:50.430
The god's preserve you.

2081
02:24:53.300 --> 02:24:57.600
It is in vain; he will not speak to you.

2082
02:25:02.770 --> 02:25:04.170
Sir,

2083
02:25:04.170 --> 02:25:06.430
We have a maid in Mytilene, I durst wager,

2084
02:25:06.430 --> 02:25:09.000
Would win some words of him.

2085
02:25:09.000 --> 02:25:10.200
'Tis well bethought.

2086
02:25:10.200 --> 02:25:12.070
She questionless with her sweet harmony

2087
02:25:12.070 --> 02:25:14.370
And other chosen attractions, would allure,

2088
02:25:14.370 --> 02:25:16.570
And make a battery through his deafen'd parts,

2089
02:25:16.570 --> 02:25:20.400
Which now are midway stopp'd:

2090
02:25:20.400 --> 02:25:22.770
She is all happy as the fairest of all,

2091
02:25:22.770 --> 02:25:24.730
And, with her fellow maids is now upon

2092
02:25:24.730 --> 02:25:26.670
The leafy shelter that abuts against

2093
02:25:26.670 --> 02:25:28.100
The island's side.

2094
02:25:28.100 --> 02:25:30.630
Sure, all's effectless; yet nothing we'll omit

2095
02:25:30.630 --> 02:25:33.370
That bears recovery's name. But, since your kindness

2096
02:25:33.370 --> 02:25:35.700
We have stretch'd thus far, let us beseech you

2097
02:25:35.700 --> 02:25:38.470
That for our gold we may provision have,

2098
02:25:38.470 --> 02:25:40.330
Wherein we are not destitute for want,

2099
02:25:40.330 --> 02:25:43.430
But weary for the staleness.

2100
02:25:43.430 --> 02:25:44.530
O, sir, a courtesy

2101
02:25:44.530 --> 02:25:46.900
Which if we should deny, the most just gods

2102
02:25:46.900 --> 02:25:48.870
For every graff would send a caterpillar,

2103
02:25:48.870 --> 02:25:55.500
And so afflict our province. Yet once more

2104
02:25:55.500 --> 02:25:58.200
Let me entreat to know at large the cause

2105
02:25:58.200 --> 02:26:00.570
Of your king's sorrow.

2106
02:26:00.570 --> 02:26:03.870
Sit, sir, I will recount it to you:

2107
02:26:09.570 --> 02:26:12.170
But, see, I am prevented.

2108
02:26:12.170 --> 02:26:13.200
O, here is

2109
02:26:13.200 --> 02:26:17.930
The lady that I sent for. Welcome, fair one!

2110
02:26:19.630 --> 02:26:21.000
Is't not a goodly presence?

2111
02:26:21.000 --> 02:26:25.370
She's a gallant lady.

2112
02:26:25.370 --> 02:26:27.030
She's such a one, that, were I well assured

2113
02:26:27.030 --> 02:26:30.100
Came of a gentle kind and noble stock,

2114
02:26:30.100 --> 02:26:34.500
I'ld wish no better choice, and think me rarely wed.

2115
02:26:42.670 --> 02:26:48.230
Fair one, all goodness that consists in bounty

2116
02:26:48.230 --> 02:26:53.970
Expect even here, where is a kingly patient:

2117
02:26:55.970 --> 02:26:58.270
If that thy prosperous and artificial feat

2118
02:26:58.270 --> 02:27:01.630
Can draw him but to answer thee in aught,

2119
02:27:01.630 --> 02:27:04.700
Thy sacred physic shall receive such pay

2120
02:27:04.700 --> 02:27:07.200
As thy desires can wish.

2121
02:27:07.200 --> 02:27:08.500
Sir, I will use

2122
02:27:08.500 --> 02:27:10.970
My utmost skill in his recovery,

2123
02:27:10.970 --> 02:27:13.700
Provided that none but I and my companion maid

2124
02:27:13.700 --> 02:27:16.130
Be suffer'd to come near him.

2125
02:27:16.130 --> 02:27:19.470
Come, let us leave her;

2126
02:27:19.470 --> 02:27:21.770
And the gods make her prosperous!

2127
02:27:43.570 --> 02:27:53.200
